title: The High Priestess
description: The Priestess sits firmly and confidently, clutching a scroll with both hands. The Moon is a symbol of illumination and intuition, illuminating a path through the dark. The scene is balanced by the two columns standing guard at either side of her one labeled _B_ and the other _J_. The Priestess represents strong, feminine energy emphasizing balance  and duality. From masculinity and femininity, good and evil, light and dark - there is an instinctive understanding that neither can exist without the other.
